title: My Dubstep Track Thingy (clip)

embed.description: I hope this will be a thing at some point :) Sorry, I kinda gave up on 'Starlights' for now

body:
Well, this is 'Miscellaneous' so I hope it includes off-topic...

What do you guys think? This is my somewhat very first dubstep track...in fact it's not even near completed...

But top 2 artists EVER TO BE BORN on Monstercat (and other places) are Au5 and Fractal. Listen to their stuff, it's real quality EDM and they usually do collabs :D

(btw drumstep is essentially dubstep just with slightly different drum sequence/etc)
